# Apptainer image definition for reproducible bioinformatics software dependencies
#
# To build container `c.sif` based on definition file `c.def`:
#   $ apptainer build c.sif c.def
#   $ apptainer inspect c.sif
#
# To execute or run commands within the container
# (docs.alliancecan.ca/wiki/Apptainer#Running_programs_within_a_container):
#   $ apptainer exec bfx.sif <bash commands>
#   $ apptainer run bfx.sif
#
# @TODO: Interactively use an image with bind paths (-B) via `apptainer shell`
